dialogue: It must be difficult to be single in the age of Covid-19.
I'm in contract negotiations with a semi-attractive woman I met online.
With any luck, I will be enjoying a double-masked goodnight kiss by late next month.
That assumes our lawyers don't make too many changes to the contract.
Did you just say she is only semi-attractive?
I'm judging from the parts I can see. I don't know what's under the mask and shower cap she wears all day.
I like the one I can see. The other one has a patch.
